walking down the street</i>


3
00:00:25.638 --> 00:00:28.850
<i>Fall in line
just watching all their feet</i>


4
00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:31.311
<i>They don't know
where they want to go</i>


5
00:00:31.394 --> 00:00:33.897
<i>But they're walking in time</i>

6
00:00:33.980 --> 00:00:36.941
<i>They got the beat
They got the beat</i>


7
