<i>They got the beat, yeah
They got the beat</i>


8
00:00:48.244 --> 00:00:51.373
<i>All the kids
just gettin' out of school</i>


9
00:00:51.456 --> 00:00:54.626
<i>They can't wait
to hang out and be cool</i>


10
00:00:54.709 --> 00:01:00.006
<i>Hang around 'til quarter after 12:00
That's when they fall in line</i>


11
