<i>Kids got the beat, yeah
Kids got the beat</i>


13
00:01:31.413 --> 00:01:34.332
<i>Go-go music
really makes us dance</i>


14
00:01:34.416 --> 00:01:38.336
<i>Do the Pony
puts us in a trance</i>


15
00:01:38.378 --> 00:01:42.924
<i>Do the Watusi, just give us a chance
That's when we fall in line</i>


16
00:01:43.008 --> 00:01:45.760
<i>'Cause we got the beat
We got the beat</i>


17
00:01:45.844 --> 00:01:51.182
<i>We got the beat, yeah
We got it</i>


18
